y:Helvetica;\ncolor:#444444\">Business Transfers<o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 3.95pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:\n5.5pt;font-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\nmso-bidi-font-family:Helvetica;color:#444444\">Information submitted through\nthis Website is a business asset of BangladesherKhbaor site and will become\npart of its normal business records. Your Personal Information may be\ntransferred to another entity (either an affiliated entity or an unrelated\nthird party) in connection with a merger, reorganization, dissolution or\nsimilar corporate event. In the event of a merger, liquidation, dissolution, or\nsale or transfer of substantially all of the assets of BangladesherKhbaor site,\nPersonal Information and/or Usage Data collected from you or about you may be\nsold, assigned, or transferred to the party acquiring all or substantially all\nof the equity and/or assets of BangladesherKhbaor site to permit the party to\ncontinue the operation of the Website, including the restricted areas. Subject\nto your ability to opt-out, by using this Website and submitting your\ninformation to us, you consent to the sale and transfer of your Personal\nInformation as described in this paragraph.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 3.95pt 0in; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><b><span style=\"font-size:7.0pt;font-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:Helvetica;\ncolor:#444444\">Government and Legal Disclosures<o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 3.95pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:\n5.5pt;font-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\nmso-bidi-font-family:Helvetica;color:#444444\">We may disclose the Personal\nInformation we collect through this Website, when we, in good faith, believe\ndisclosure is appropriate to comply with the law (or a court order or subpoena),\nto prevent or investigate a possible crime, such as fraud or identity theft, to\nenforce our Terms and Conditions or other agreements that govern your use of\nthis Website, or to protect the rights, property or safety of The BangladesherKhbaor\nsite, our members or others.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 7.9pt 0in 3.95pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><b><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:Helvetica;\ncolor:#444444\">VI. Privacy Notices<o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 3.95pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:\n5.5pt;font-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\nmso-bidi-font-family:Helvetica;color:#444444\">This Privacy Policy may be\nsupplemented or amended from time to time by \"privacy notices\" posted\non this Website. For example, certain pages of this Website contain privacy\nnotices providing details about the personal information we collect on those\npages, why we need that information, and choices you may have about the ways we\nuse that information.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 7.9pt 0in 3.95pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><b><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:Helvetica;\ncolor:#444444\">VII. The Choices You Have<o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 3.95pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:\n5.5pt;font-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\nmso-bidi-font-family:Helvetica;color:#444444\">BangladesherKhbaor site respects\nyour right to make choices about the ways we collect, use and disclose your\nPersonal Information. We generally ask you to indicate your choices at the time\nand on the page where you provide your Personal Information. You may browse\nthis Website without providing any information that identifies you personally\nand may choose not to provide the information we request, although this may\nmean that you can not make a purchase or take advantage of other features of\nthis Website. You may cancel your registration to any part of the Website at\nany time by following the appropriate instructions contained on the Website.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 7.9pt 0in 3.95pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><b><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:Helvetica;\ncolor:#444444\">VIII. Unsolicited Comments and Feedback<o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 3.95pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:\n5.5pt;font-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\nmso-bidi-font-family:Helvetica;color:#444444\">Unless subject to a separate\nagreement between you and BangladesherKhbaor site, any feedback, data, answers,\nquestions, comments, suggestions, ideas or the like (collectively,\n\"Feedback\") that you send to us through this Website will be treated\nas non-confidential and nonproprietary. We assume no obligation to protect such\nFeedback from disclosure and are free to reproduce, use and distribute the\nFeedback to others for any purpose and without restriction. By submitting\nFeedback through this Website, you are granting BangladesherKhbaor site a\nnon-exclusive, unrestricted, perpetual and irrevocable license to use your\nFeedback and any related know-how for any purpose whatsoever, without\ncompensating you in any way, including, but not limited to, developing and\nmarketing products and services incorporating such Feedback.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 7.9pt 0in 3.95pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><b><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:Helvetica;\ncolor:#444444\">IX. Security<o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 3.95pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:\n5.5pt;font-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\nmso-bidi-font-family:Helvetica;color:#444444\">We use industry-standard\nencryption technologies when transferring and receiving payment data. We have\nsecurity measures in place to protect against the loss, misuse or alteration of\npersonal information that we have collected from or about you. We are in\ncompliance with the Health Insurance Portability and Accountability Act for any\ndata that we may collect that is subject to this regulation. It is important\nthat you understand, however, that no Website or database is completely secure\nor \"hacker proof.\" You are also responsible for taking reasonable steps\nto protect your Personal Information against unauthorized disclosure or misuse,\nfor example, by protecting your passwords. We take seriously the security of\nthe information we collect. BangladesherKhbaor site has therefore implemented\ntechnology and security policies and procedures intended to reduce the risk of\naccidental destruction or loss, or the unauthorized disclosure or access to,\nsuch information, reasonably appropriate to the nature of the data concerned.\nIf we believe that the security of information that you have provided to us has\nbeen compromised, we may notify you by e-mail, if we have your email address.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 7.9pt 0in 3.95pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><b><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:Helvetica;\ncolor:#444444\">X. Changes And Updates to This Privacy Policy<o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 3.95pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:\n5.5pt;font-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\nmso-bidi-font-family:Helvetica;color:#444444\">We reserve the right to update or\nmodify this Privacy Policy, at any time and without prior notice, by posting a\nrevised version of this Privacy Policy on the Website. The revised version of\nthe Privacy Policy will be effective as of the date that we post it on this\nWebsite. Your use of this Website following a revision of the Privacy Policy\nconstitutes your agreement that all Personal Information collected from or\nabout you through this Website after the revised Privacy Policy is posted is\nsubject to the terms of the revised Privacy Policy. We urge each visitor to\nrefer back to this page regularly and especially prior to providing or updating\nany Personal Information. This Policy may not be otherwise amended without the\nwritten consent of BangladesherKhbaor site. You may access the current version\nof this Privacy Policy at any time by clicking on the link marked \"Privacy\nPolicy\" at the bottom of each page of this Website.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 7.9pt 0in 3.95pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><b><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:Helvetica;\ncolor:#444444\">XI. Our Policy Regarding Children and Minors<o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 3.95pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:\n5.5pt;font-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\nmso-bidi-font-family:Helvetica;color:#444444\">This Website is not directed at\nminors (under the age of 13) or generally intended for use by children under\nthe age of 13. We do not knowingly collect Personal Information from children\nin this age group. We ask that if you are a minor you not submit any personal\ninformation to us. If your children disclose information about themselves in\npublicly accessible areas of the Website, they may receive unsolicited messages\nfrom other persons. Please tell them not to do so.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 7.9pt 0in 3.95pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><b><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:Helvetica;\ncolor:#444444\">XII. Questions<o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 3.95pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:\n5.5pt;font-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\nmso-bidi-font-family:Helvetica;color:#444444\">If at any time you believe the BangladesherKhbaor\nSites have not adhered to these principles, please notify us by e-mail to news.bk.bnel@gmail.comand\nwe will use all commercially reasonable efforts to promptly determine and\ncorrect the problem.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 3.95pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:\n5.5pt;font-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\nmso-bidi-font-family:Helvetica;color:#444444\">If you have any more questions\nabout this policy please email us at news.bk.bnel@gmail.com or write to<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><span style=\"font-size:7.0pt;font-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">BangladesherKhbaor <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><span style=\"font-size:7.0pt;font-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">1 R. K. Mission Road (2nd Floor) <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><span style=\"font-size:7.0pt;font-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">Dhaka-1203, Bangladesh <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><span style=\"font-size:7.0pt;font-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">Tel : +88-02-57164681-3 <o:p></o:p></span></p><p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n</p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><span style=\"font-size:7.0pt;font-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">Email: news.bk.bnel@gmail.com&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>', 5, '2016-10-01 20:30:37', '', 'Disclaimer & Privacy Policy', NULL, NULL);
